Print method for class

Usage

# S3 method for class 'osrs_api'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

object of class osrs_api

...

additional arguments passed to methods

Examples

whip <- osrs_api(items = "Abyssal_whip", history = "latest")
print(whip)
